                                              Colleen Walsh, "An Unexpected Juxtaposition", <em>The Harvard Gazette</em> (June 7, 2019), [e-journal], https://news.harvard.edu/gazette/story/2019/06/harvard-art-museums-challenges-expectations-with-new-art-pairing/, accessed June 10, 2019
